-- EIH Rights Offer May Help Reliance Raise Stake, E Times Reports
-- Suprotip Ghosh
-- 2010-09-21T01:35:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/eih-rights-offer-may-help-reliance-industries-raise-stake-e-times-reports.html

          
          
             A rights offer by EIH Ltd, owner of
India’s Oberoi and the Trident hotel chains, may allow the
Mukesh Ambani-controlled Reliance group to increase its holding
from 14.8 percent, the Economic Times reported, citing analysts
it didn’t identify..  
